[32m+[m[32m  * **Interactive Study Planner (Cognitive Load Balancer):** Tailored schedules preventing burnout.[m
[32m+[m[32m  * **Comprehensive Analytics:** Visual dashboards tracking performance and content depth.[m
[32m+[m[32m* **Speaker Notes:**[m
[32m+[m[32m  > "At its core, the platform features smart document processing. You upload a syllabus or a PDF, and the engine digests it. It then dynamically generates interactive assessments including Short Answer modes with strict Professor-style grading. We've also built an adaptive study planner powered by Cognitive Load Balancing to keep students from burning out, alongside a data-rich analytics dashboard to visualize progress over time."[m
[32m+[m
