[32m+[m[32m  * **AI Viva Mode:** Complete speech-to-text pipeline simulating real oral exams.[m
[32m+[m[32m  * **Offline/Privacy-First Processing:** Fast local audio extraction (Whisper + FFmpeg).[m
[32m+[m[32m* **Speaker Notes:**[m
